 aims for Paris 2024 are building public pools on the River Seine and also converting the areas around Olympic venues into new neighborhoods.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2517, \"end\": 2527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2459095198873772e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main legacy\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"public pools\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"the areas\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"new neighborhoods\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ensuring the Games are remembered for their sustainability achievements is another ambition - and one that the organizers consider just as important.\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"their sustainability achievements\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"another ambition\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Subscribe toStoryboard: A weekly newsletterbringing you the best of CGTN every Friday SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyrig